    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not just self-pity though. it feels heavier than that. i look at them and i just see how much easier their lives would be if they didn't have to worry about me constantly. if i wasn't a constant source of stress and extra work for them. sometimes i think it would be more selfless to just... not be around to cause all that trouble.",
